% About 

Aurica is a translator AI bot capable of accurately translating text from Spanish, French, German, and Portuguese into English and vice versa 
with a focus on fluency, contextual understanding, and natural language processing.

%% Demo: 

Try out the translator here:- https://illa.ai/ai-agent/ILAex4p1C7Yg/detail

%% Example of how it works: 

User:
olá, como vai? você está triste?

Aurica
Hello! I'm doing well, thank you. As an AI, I don't have feelings, so I cannot be sad or happy. Is there anything I can help you with?

User
Welche Farbe hat der Himmel?

Aurica
The color of the sky is typically blue. Is there anything else you would like to know?
